[package]
name = "jellyfin-api"
version = "0.1.0"
authors = [ "OpenAPI Generator team and contributors",]
description = "No description provided (generated by Openapi Generator https://github.com/openapitools/openapi-generator)"
license = "MIT"
edition = "2021"

[dependencies]
serde_json = "^1.0"
serde_repr = "^0.1"
url = "^2.5"

[dependencies.serde]
version = "^1.0"
features = [ "derive",]

[dependencies.serde_with]
version = "^3.8"
default-features = false
features = [ "base64", "std", "macros",]

[dependencies.uuid]
version = "^1.8"
features = [ "serde", "v4",]

[dependencies.reqwest]
version = "^0.12"
features = [ "json", "multipart",]

[package]
name = "qcm-plugin-jellyfin"
version = "0.1.0"
authors = [ "hypengw <hypengwip@gmail.com>",]
edition = "2021"

[dependencies]
log = "0.4"
async-trait = "0.1"
anyhow = "1.0"
uuid = "1"

[dependencies.qcm-core]
git = "https://github.com/hypengw/QcmBackend.git"

[dependencies.sea-orm]
version = "1"

[dependencies.serde_json]
version = "1.0"

[dependencies.chrono]
version = "0.4"

[dependencies.reqwest]
version = "0.12"

[dependencies.jellyfin-api]
path = "./jellyfin-api"

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.28"
features = [ "full",]

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0"
features = [ "derive",]

[dependencies.rust-embed]
version = "8.6"
features = [ "interpolate-folder-path",]
